    <h1 class="display-lg post-title">How to Remove PMI: Your Complete Guide to Eliminating Mortgage Insurance</h1>
    <div class="post-byline"><span class="mono">By Jim Blackburn · NMLS #1072866</span><span class="post-byline__sep">·</span><time datetime="2025-11-05">2025-11-05</time></div>
  </header>

